	<li id="text-7" class="widget widget_text"><h2 class="widgettitle">About the author</h2>
			<div class="textwidget"><a href="http://women4hope.files.wordpress.com/2007/11/picture-54.jpg" title="picture-54.jpg"><img src="http://women4hope.files.wordpress.com/2007/11/picture-54.thumbnail.jpg" alt="picture-54.jpg" /></a>

My name is Catherine Morgan, I'm a writer, nurse, and mother.  I'm also living with Chronic Fatigue Syndrome and other chronic illnesses.  I hope this will be a site where patients, family, and medical professionals can find information, ideas, inspiration, and hope.  

