	<img alt='' src='http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/688713a1687e53fcc8a6c0e486f5cb49?s=32&amp;d=identicon&amp;r=G' class='avatar avatar-32' height='32' width='32' />	<h3 class="commenttitle"><cite class="fn"><a href='http://www.pinkmini.wordpress.com' rel='external nofollow' class='url'>pinkmini</a></cite> <span class="says">said</span></h3>
